CEZ Gets Ministry Approval for Heating Line, Lidove Noviny Says

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-02-24T07:18:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/cez-gets-ministry-approval-for-heating-line-lidove-noviny-says.html
  CEZ AS , the  Czech Republic ’s biggest
power utility, got permission from the environment ministry to
build a pipeline supplying heat from its Temelin nuclear plant
to South Bohemia’s regional capital Ceske Budejovice, Lidove
Noviny  reported , citing Temelin spokesman Marek Svitak.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
